{"tid":1475363,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[目標明確]星期日係公關示威！","createTime":"2019-08-15T12:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T11:47:26.000Z","uid":87134,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6bbade84866e41fd0edd3e670c8682cd86b8558a","tid":1475363,"uid":87134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:42:22.000Z","msg":"星期日嘅和理非示威好重要！<br />\n而家運動對啲淺黃淺藍中立派嚟講有啲失焦<br />\n我地手足比人射到盲咗<br />\n荃灣比人斬到開花<br />\n元朗黑社會全部未告<br />\n有中聯辦葉虎同公安插手嘅嫌疑<br />\n好似都無受到應有關注<br />\n星期日就係要將個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">焦點放返喺警察同政府度</span></span><br />\n<br />\n加上呢排衝突多咗<br />\n少咗和理非出嚟<br />\n亦都得失咗某啲中立派<br />\n<br />\n星期日嘅目標就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聚焦</span></span><br />\n同埋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公關</span></span><br />\n<br />\n既然星期日有呢個目標就要堅持打好公關打到底<br />\n就算陣係批我喺個公廁集會<br />\n我都會留喺個公廁成日！<br />\n<br />\n我地係共同體<br />\n手足做咩打死我都唔會割席架啦<br />\n不過如果有手足太激動未必達到星期日嘅目標<br />\n我會盡量阻止<br />\n<br />\n要贏<br />\n就要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">能屈能伸</span></span><br />\n香港人一定會睇到最後嘅勝利架<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">818 香港人Assemble!!!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa5b1908e4ac24cb4a7d64813ff0c937cc0f24a","tid":1475363,"uid":87134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:45:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff426e7c7c82c3ecb62c28dd63126706f00f263c","tid":1475363,"uid":87134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:46:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09dcb86924ac475911378335896afde75034a81a","tid":1475363,"uid":277519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"推。支持<img src=\"/assets/faces